        "timestamp": "2022-05-23 17:00:30.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nThis is with regards to \n\nhttps://jira.linuxfoundation.org/plugins/servlet/theme/portal/2/IT-24061\n\nBasic jenkins build failures started to occur on May, 15th.   I suspect some underlying changes in the infrastructure.\n\nTrying to test if indicating JVM to use IPv4 may solve the problem on Jenkins servers.\n\nPlease advice.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
